---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Copes' Islander — Oceanfront Vacation Rental, Comox Valley BC"
  description="Copes' Islander is an oceanfront vacation rental on Vancouver Island, Comox Valley, BC. Inquire to book your stay."
>
  <section
    class="relative flex items-center justify-center min-h-[80vh] overflow-hidden"
    style="background-image: url('/photos/IMG_0284.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/15 via-black/30 to-black/50"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-6xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight text-cream-warm leading-[1.1] [text-shadow:0_2px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.6)]">
        Oceanfront. The Comox Valley way.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-lg md:text-xl text-cream-warm/90 mt-6 [text-shadow:0_1px_4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
        A real oceanfront rental in the Comox Valley. Two bedrooms, full kitchen, private beach access.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-10">
        <a
          href="/suite"
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-rust text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-rust-soft transition-colors"
        >
          See rates
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="px-8 py-3 bg-white/90 text-navy font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-white transition-colors"
        >
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream py-24 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Section header (centered, above two-column layout) -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wider text-rust uppercase">
          AROUND THE PROPERTY
        </p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-navy tracking-tight mt-3">
          A few moments from the place
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Two-column composition: hosts left (larger), polaroids right (smaller) -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-x-12 gap-y-12 items-start">

        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: hosts placeholder + paragraph (md:col-span-7) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-8">

          <!-- Big hosts placeholder polaroid -->
          <div class="bg-white p-3 pb-12 shadow-lg rotate-[-1deg] max-w-md mx-auto">
            <div class="w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-cream-warm border-2 border-dashed border-stone/40 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center px-6">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs tracking-widest text-stone uppercase mb-2">Placeholder</p>
                <p class="font-serif italic text-lg text-stone">Mike &amp; Patti<br/>photo coming soon</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="font-serif italic text-sm text-stone text-center mt-4">your hosts</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Hosts paragraph -->
          <div class="max-w-md mx-auto px-2">
            <p class="font-serif italic text-lg text-navy leading-relaxed">
              We&rsquo;re Mike and Patti &mdash; hosts at Copes&rsquo; Islander since 1996. The day jobs are behind us, the kids are grown and gone, but we&rsquo;re still here on the strait. Welcoming guests from around the world has been a pleasure we&rsquo;ve never tired of.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: 2x2 polaroid grid (md:col-span-5) -->
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">

            <div class="bg-white p-2 pb-8 shadow-md rotate-[-1deg]">
              <img src="/photos/IMG_0278.jpg" alt="The exterior of the property" class="w-full aspect-[1/1] object-cover" />
              <p class="font-serif italic text-xs text-stone text-center mt-3">the place itself</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-2 pb-8 shadow-md rotate-[1deg]">
              <img src="/photos/steps_to_beach.jpg" alt="Stone steps from the deck down to the rocky beach" class="w-full aspect-[1/1] object-cover" />
              <p class="font-serif italic text-xs text-stone text-center mt-3">down to the water</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-2 pb-8 shadow-md rotate-[1deg]">
              <img src="/photos/twilight_sky.jpg" alt="Twilight sky over the property and shoreline" class="w-full aspect-[1/1] object-cover" />
              <p class="font-serif italic text-xs text-stone text-center mt-3">sky show, every night</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-2 pb-8 shadow-md rotate-[-1deg]">
              <img src="/photos/corner_window.jpg" alt="View from the corner window of the suite" class="w-full aspect-[1/1] object-cover" />
              <p class="font-serif italic text-xs text-stone text-center mt-3">the view from the couch</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-wider text-rust uppercase mb-3">
        WHERE WE ARE
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy tracking-tight mb-12">
        A few minutes from the ferry, the winery, and the strait
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/photos/map-osm.png"
            alt="Map showing Copes' Islander at 1484 Wilkinson Road, Comox, BC, on the coast near Little River"
            class="w-full aspect-[1005/644] object-cover border-4 border-cream-warm shadow-md"
          />
          {/* marker */}
          <div class="absolute" style="left: 47.8%; top: 59.0%; transform: translate(-50%, -100%);">
            <svg width="28" height="36" viewBox="0 0 28 36" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.35));">
              <path d="M14 0C6.3 0 0 6.3 0 14c0 10.5 14 22 14 22s14-11.5 14-22C28 6.3 21.7 0 14 0z" fill="#b8552c"/>
              <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="5" fill="#f5f1e8"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-stone italic text-center mt-4">
          Just off Wilkinson Road in the Comox Valley.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=1484+Wilkinson+Rd+Comox+BC" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block mt-2 font-sans text-sm text-navy hover:text-rust transition-colors underline underline-offset-4 decoration-stone/40 hover:decoration-rust">
          Get directions →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-navy leading-relaxed">
        Step off the deck and onto the beach. Watch the Powell River ferry come in. Dig clams at low tide; paddle a canoe at high. Salmon jump within feet of the shore. Evening sunsets are followed by starlit nights and a passing parade of cruise ships plying the waters of Georgia Strait on their way to Alaska.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
